---
title: "Register"
description: "Register for the next Fight for Manhood cohort."
layout: "base.njk"
permalink: "/register/"
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <h1 class="h1">Register</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Wednesdays at 6:00 PM in Knoxville. 10-week cohort. No cost.
    </p>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <form
      name="ffm-register"
      method="POST"
      data-netlify="true"
      data-netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
      action="/success/"
      class="form card"
    >
      <!-- Netlify form-name (required) -->
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="ffm-register" />

      <!-- Honeypot -->
      <p class="sr-only">
        <label>Don’t fill this out if you’re human: <input name="bot-field" /></label>
      </p>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="name">Full name</label>
        <input id="name" name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" required />
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="email">Email</label>
        <input id="email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required />
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="phone">Phone (optional)</label>
        <input id="phone" name="phone" type="tel" autocomplete="tel" />
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="notes">Anything we should know? (optional)</label>
        <textarea id="notes" name="notes" rows="4" placeholder="Questions, concerns, anything you want to share."></textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="actions">
        <button class="btn primary" type="submit">Submit Registration</button>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="/">Back to Home</a>
      </div>

      <p class="fineprint">
        By registering, you’re asking for a spot in the next cohort. We’ll confirm details by email/text.
      </p>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section { padding: 64px 0; }
  .container { width: min(1100px, calc(100% - 48px)); margin: 0 auto; }
  .narrow { width: min(720px, calc(100% - 48px)); }
  .h1 { font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 52px); line-height: 1.05; margin: 0 0 10px; }
  .lead { font-size: 18px; opacity: .9; margin: 0 0 18px; }
  .divider { height: 1px; width: 100%; margin: 22px 0 28px; background: rgba(212,175,55,.35); box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(212,175,55,.12); }
  .card { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10); background: rgba(0,0,0,.25); border-radius: 18px; padding: 22px; }
  .form { display: grid; gap: 14px; }
  label { display: block; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 6px; }
  input, textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px 12px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
    background: rgba(0,0,0,.35);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
    outline: none;
  }
  input:focus, textarea:focus { border-color: rgba(212,175,55,.55); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(212,175,55,.14); }
  .actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 6px; }
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
    text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .02em;
  }
  .btn.primary { background: rgba(212,175,55,.95); color: #0b1220; border-color: rgba(212,175,55,.95); }
  .btn.ghost { background: transparent; color: rgba(255,255,255,.92); }
  .fineprint { font-size: 13px; opacity: .75; margin: 4px 0 0; }
  .sr-only { position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: auto; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden; }
</style>
